item.dc:creator: @Loveandpower Loveandpower
item.description:
@Loveandpower wrote:

[quote=“own master, post:1, topic:394472”]hey guys i have this problem i wanna make my server not too easy to level up and not too hard ive done all the other skills but these ones i can’t seem to find where it is set any ideas??[/quote]You can find your skills in

src-server-models-players-skills if it is a pi

you can edit the skill multiplier in config.java

to get even more specific you can edit most of them in actionhandler.java
